                        <p><span t-field="doc.first_name"/> <span t-field="doc.last_name"/></p>
                        <p><span t-field="doc.present_address"/></p>
                        <p style="text-align: center;"><strong>MEMO FOR REGULARIZATION</strong></p>
                        <br/>
                        <p>We are glad to inform you that  effective <span t-field="doc.date_hired"/> 
                        your employment with NDM SANCHEZ BUILDERS AND DEVELOPMENT CORPORATION is now 
                        <strong>REGULAR</strong>, under the following condition:</p>
                        <ol class='a m-left-62'>
                            <li>
                                <p class='m-left-16'> 
                                Your official designation in the company in the company is
                                <span t-field="doc.job_id"/> with a monthly basic rate of 
                                <strong> Php <t t-esc="'{:,.2f}'.format(doc.contract_id.wage)"/></strong> and 
                                <strong>Php <t t-esc="'{:,.2f}'.format(doc.contract_id.allowance)"/> </strong>
                                monthly allowance at the date herein stated.</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p class='m-left-16'>You agree to abide by the job description discussed to
                                you on your hiring date or with any other related work which may arise from 
                                time to time or as instructed directly by your immediate superior.</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p class='m-left-16'>You agree to devote full time working hours to the company.</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p class='m-left-16'>You agree that information, records and documents of the company are confidential information, and 
                                unauthorized copying of the company records is sufficient cause for the company to terminate your service immediately. </p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p class='m-left-16'>You agree that all the company assets, records and documents used by you shall be surrendered upon request 
                                by your immediate superior and under same circumstances shall be returned by you upon termination of your work from the company.</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                  <p class='m-left-16'>You are bound to agree, familiarize and abide by all company Policies and rule written on the employee Handbook.</p>
                            </li>
                        </ol>
                        
                        <p>If the above terms and condition are applicable, please indicate your acceptance by signing on the space provided below.</p>
